Shipped 5 antifeature fixes + 1 new feature:

CULLED:
1. eywa_agents: was unbounded (all memories, no limit). Now 24h window + 500 row cap + splits active vs recent.

5. eywa_sync: was unbounded session history. Now capped at 100 rows.

ADDED:
